teOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n37:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n38:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n39:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n40:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n41: }\n42: ```\n43: \n44: #### AgentRuntime Methods\n45: \n46: **Create**\n47: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.CreateOptions`\n48: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n49: - **Description**: Create a new AgentRuntime resource\n50: \n51: **Update**\n52: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n53: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n54: - **Description**: Update an existing AgentRuntime resource\n55: \n56: **UpdateStatus**\n57: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n58: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n59: - **Description**: Update the status subresource of an AgentRuntime\n60: \n61: **Delete**\n62: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.DeleteOptions`\n63: - **Returns**: `error`\n64: - **Description**: Delete an AgentRuntime resource by name\n65: \n66: **Get**\n67: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.GetOptions`\n68: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n69: - **Description**: Get an AgentRuntime resource by name\n70: \n71: **List**\n72: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n73: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList`, `error`\n74: - **Description**: List AgentRuntime resources\n75: \n76: **Watch**\n77: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n78: - **Returns**: `watch.Interface`, `error`\n79: - **Description**: Watch for AgentRuntime resource changes\n80: \n81: **Patch**\n82: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `pt types.PatchType`, `data []byte`, `opts metav1.PatchOptions`, `subresources ...string`\n83: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n84: - **Description**: Patch an AgentRuntime resource\n85: \n86: ### CodeInterpreter Client\n87: \n88: #### CodeInterpreterInterface\n89: \n90: ```go\n91: type CodeInterpreterInterface interface {\n92:     Create(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n93:     Update(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n94:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n95:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n96:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, listOpts metav1.ListOptions, deleteOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n97:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n98:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList, error)\n99:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n100:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n101: }\n102: ```\n103: \n104: #### CodeInterpreter Methods\n105: \n106: **Create**\n107: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `opts metav1.CreateOptions`\n108: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n109: - **Description**: Create a new CodeInterpreter resource\n110: \n111: **Update**\n112: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n113: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n114: - **Description**: Update an existing CodeInterpreter resource\n115: \n116: **UpdateStatus**\n117: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n118: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n119: - **Description**: Update the status subresource of a CodeInterpreter\n120: \n121: **Delete**\n122: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.DeleteOptions`\n123: - **Returns**: `error`\n124: - **Description**: Delete a CodeInterpreter resource by name\n125: \n126: **Get**\n127: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.GetOptions`\n128: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n129: - **Description**: Get a CodeInterpreter resource by name\n130: \n131: **List**\n132: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n133: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList`, `error`\n134: - **Description**: List CodeInterpreter resources\n135: \n136: **Watch**\n137: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n138: - **Returns**: `watch.Interface`, `error`\n139: - **Description**: Watch for CodeInterpreter resource changes\n140: \n141: **Patch**\n142: - **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `pt types.PatchType`, `data []byte`, `opts metav1.PatchOptions`, `subresources ...string`\n143: - **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n144: - **Description**: Patch a CodeInterpreter resource\n145: \n146: ### Informer\n147: \n148: #### AgentRuntimeInformer\n149: \n150: ```go\n151: type AgentRuntimeInformer interface {\n152:     Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n153:     Lister() runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister\n154: }\n155: ```\n156: \n157: #### CodeInterpreterInformer\n158: \n159: ```go\n160: type CodeInterpreterInformer interface {\n161:     Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n162:     Lister() runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterLister\n163: }\n164: ```\n165: \n166: ### Lister\n167: \n168: #### AgentRuntimeLister\n169: \n170: ```go\n171: type AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n172:     List(selector labels.Selector) (ret []*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, err error)\n173:     AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n174:     AgentRuntimeListerExpansion\n175: }\n176: ```\n177: \n178: #### CodeInterpreterLister\n179: \n180: ```go\n181: type CodeInterpreterLister interface {\n182:     List(selector labels.Selector) (ret []*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, err error)\n183:     CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister\n184:     CodeInterpreterListerExpansion\n185: }\n186: ```\n187: \n188: ## Common Types\n189: \n190: ### API Verbs\n191: \n192: Common verbs for API operations:\n193: - `create` - Create a resource\n194: - `update` - Update a resource\n195: - `delete` - Delete a resource\n196: - `get` - Get a single resource\n197: - `list` - List multiple resources\n198: - `watch` - Watch for resource changes\n199: - `patch` - Patch a resource\n200: \n201: ### Context\n202: \n203: All client methods accept a `context.Context` for:\n204: - Request cancellation\n205: - Timeout control\n206: - Request-scoped values\n207: \n208: ### Error Handling\n209: \n210: All client methods return `error` for:\n211: - Network errors\n212: - API errors\n213: - Validation errors\n214: - Authentication/authorization errors\n215: \n216: ## Best Practices\n217: \n218: - Always provide context to client methods\n219: - Use proper error handling\n220: - Implement retry logic for transient failures\n221: - Use Listers for read-only operations when possible\n222: - Use Informers for event-driven workflows\n223: - Clean up resources properly (e.g., stop informers)\n224: - Use proper timeouts for long-running operations\n\n(End of file - total 224 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 Specification\n\n## Module: client-go\n\n### ClientSet\n\n#### ClientSet Definition\n\n```go\ntype Interface interface {\n    Runtime() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n    Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n}\n```\n\n#### RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n\n```go\ntype RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n    RESTClient() rest.Interface","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/spec.md","time":{"start":1775888020471,"end":1775888020483}}}}
